reviewText:
T​hey never respond to questions.
They never fix problems even years later.
Excel links point to inaccessible university addresses.
The videos are long and verbose and deal with many superficial and cosmetic aspects - lightweight.
The PowerBI required for later sessions is unavailable with personal email address, no matter what they say.
They have not arranged with Microsoft for student access to the necessary Microsoft service.
The quizzes and assignments are lightweight to the extent of being trivial
The PowerBI Menus are out of date, causing great frustration and time-wasting
There is very little use of the important feature like DAX and M
